  <brief_title>Oral Glucocorticosteroid in the Treatment of Severe Asthma Exacerbation in Hospitalized Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 4, Randomized Study of Oral Glucocorticosteroid Administration in the Treatment of Acute Severe Asthma Exacerbation in Hospitalized Patients</official_title>
